# Uncommon
Show
    BaseType "Blessed Orb" "Cartographer's Chisel" "Chaos Orb" "Gemcutter's Prism" "Glassblower's Bauble" "Orb of Alchemy" "Orb of Fusing" "Orb of Regret" "Orb of Scouring" "Regal Orb" "Vaal Orb"
