    Rarity = Normal Magic
    Class "Claw" "Dagger" "Wand" "One Hand Sword" "One Hand Axe" "One Hand Mace" "Bow" "Staves" "Two Hand Sword" "Two Hand Axe" "Two Hand Mace" "Sceptre"
